@startuml
!theme plain
autonumber

actor "Shipping Agent Rep." as Actor
participant "User Interface\n(Single Page App)" as UI
participant "Backend Service\n(Port System REST API)" as Backend

Actor -> UI : 1: edit and save notification
activate UI
UI -> Backend : 1.1: Request (PUT /api/notifications/{id})
activate Backend
Backend --> UI : 1.2: Response (200 OK / 409 Conflict)
deactivate Backend
UI --> Actor : 1.3: Display confirmation or error
deactivate UI

@enduml